         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne Botan. Garden ¶ 14/1/71 ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ At a meeting of the Trustees of the Royal Park, held yesterday, it was brought under the notice of my colleagues that on the occasion of the ignition of t...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">71.01.14</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Frederick Standish</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A345 Royal Park<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Trustees<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>letter &amp; minute book, p. 49, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne Botan. Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">14/1/71</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>At a meeting of the Trustees of the Royal Park, held yesterday, it was brought under the notice of my colleagues that on the occasion of the ignition of the grass in the Park on the 11th inst., the police stationed there or in the vicinity displayed great zeal and attended most promptly to suppress the flames, and that thus the Park was saved from a general conflagration.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The fire was blamed on children playing with matches<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Argus</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Melbourne), 12 January 1871, p. 4).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have now the pleasing duty to perform to convey a resolution of the Trustees that their best thanks should be given to the police who came so promptly and zealously forward on that occasion and I now beg of you to be so kind to convey to the men of your force this expression of appreciation of their help rendered on the occasion referred to.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedt servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>F. von Mueller, Hon Sec.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Capt Standish</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Chief Commissioner of Police</p>
         </div>
